Biggest India, U.S. Aircraft Deal Under Threat, Express Reports

-- B y   R a j h k u m a r   K   S h a a w
-- 
2011-03-27T15:11:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-27/biggest-india-u-s-aircraft-deal-under-threat-express-reports.html
India ’s biggest defense deal with
the U.S. to purchase 10 C-17 Globemaster III aircraft is under
threat after the country’s Defence Ministry asked the U.S. to
disclose comparative prices at which the aircraft were sold to
other nations, the  Indian Express  reported, citing unidentified
officials.  The contract with Boeing Co. is in the final stages and
commercial negotiations have been concluded, Indian Express
said.  Link to Story: LIOOV56MBOQR  To contact the reporter on this story:
